    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are appropriately not assessed at this risk level. The CFD model is accepted as credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device within the defined COU. RH < 1 acceptance criterion is supported by validated model predictions across all five operating points.",
